## Escalation Signals (Flag Automatically)

Flag these without being asked:
- Any copy using a [hard rule violation — e.g., emdash, vague value term, regulatory language]
- Any CTA that names the action instead of the outcome
- Any error message without a recovery step
- Any empty state without an action
- Any status label that reads as raw data rather than interpreted insight
- Any copy that amplifies anxiety in a [high-stress context]
